text: Sead Marušić (born 15 December 1965) is a Croatian rower. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Yugoslavia Category:Olympic rowers of Croatia Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Split, Croatia
